            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 5100,
            "LocalizeKR": "호, 혹시\n처음부터 알고 있었던 거야……?",
            "LocalizeJP": "も、もしかして、\n最初から気づいてた……？",
            "VoiceIds": [],
            "CollectionVisible": false,
            "CVCollectionType": 0,
            "LocalizeCVGroup": "CVGroup_UILobbySpecial_Idle1",
            "AnimationName": "Talk_01_M",
            "Anniversary": 0,
            "StartDate": "",
            "EndDate": "",
            "ApplyPosition": false,
            "PosX": 0.0,
            "PosY": 0.0,
            "UnlockFavorRank": 0,
            "UnlockEquipWeapon": false
          },
          {
            "CharacterId": 10049,
            "CostumeUniqueId": 1004901,
            "DisplayOrder": 270,
            "DialogCategory": 8,
            "DialogCondition": 0,
            "GroupId": 1,
            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 9733,
            "LocalizeKR": "그런가……\n뭐, 눈치 못 챌 리가\n없긴 하겠지……",
            "LocalizeJP": "そっか……\nまあ気づいてない\nわけが無いよね……。",
            "VoiceIds": [],
            "CollectionVisible": false,
            "CVCollectionType": 0,
            "LocalizeCVGroup": "CVGroup_UILobbySpecial_Idle1",
            "AnimationName": "",
            "Anniversary": 0,
            "StartDate": "",
            "EndDate": "",
            "ApplyPosition": false,
            "PosX": 0.0,
            "PosY": 0.0,
            "UnlockFavorRank": 0,
            "UnlockEquipWeapon": false
          },
          {
            "CharacterId": 10049,
            "CostumeUniqueId": 1004901,
            "DisplayOrder": 280,
            "DialogCategory": 8,
            "DialogCondition": 0,
            "GroupId": 2,
            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 5000,
            "LocalizeKR": "아니, 별로\n피하거나 하는 건\n아닌데 말야……",
            "LocalizeJP": "いや別に、\n避けてたわけじゃ\nないんだけど……。",
            "VoiceIds": [],
            "CollectionVisible": false,
            "CVCollectionType": 0,
            "LocalizeCVGroup": "CVGroup_UILobbySpecial_Idle2",
            "AnimationName": "Talk_02_M",
            "Anniversary": 0,
            "StartDate": "",
            "EndDate": "",
            "ApplyPosition": false,
            "PosX": 0.0,
            "PosY": 0.0,
            "UnlockFavorRank": 0,
            "UnlockEquipWeapon": false
          },
          {
            "CharacterId": 10049,
            "CostumeUniqueId": 1004901,
            "DisplayOrder": 290,
            "DialogCategory": 8,
            "DialogCondition": 0,
            "GroupId": 2,
            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 12033,
            "LocalizeKR": "그냥 조금, 그……\n지금……\n쌩얼, 이니까……",
            "LocalizeJP": "ただちょっと……\nその……今……\nすっぴん、だから……。",
